description: Returns the  IPSet that is specified by IPSetId.

parameters.name: IPSetId
parameters.description: The IPSetId of the  IPSet that you want to get. IPSetId is returned by  CreateIPSet and by  ListIPSets.

nested_items.description: IPSet: Contains IPSetDescriptors, IPSetId, and Name.
IPSetDescriptors: Contains an array of  IPSetDescriptor objects. Each IPSetDescriptor object contains Type and Value.
